import React, { Fragment, useState } from 'react'
import { Button, Card, CardBody, CardTitle, Form, FormGroup, Input, Label, Row } from 'reactstrap';
import { Colxx } from '../../common/CustomBootstrap';
import CustomDropzone from '../../forms/CustomDropzone';
import "./AddUser.css";

function AddUser() {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <Row className="mb-4">
        <Colxx xxs="12">
          <Card>
            <CardBody>
              <CardTitle>
                Ajouter un utilisateur
                </CardTitle>
              <Form>
                <FormGroup row>


                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="exampleEmailGrid">
                        Prénom
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="text"
                        name="exampleEmailGrid"
                        id="exampleFirstnameGrid"
                        placeholder="foulen"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="examplePasswordGrid">
                        Nom
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="text"
                        name="exampleLastnameGrid"
                        id="exampleLastnameGrid"
                        placeholder="ben foulen"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={12}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="exampleAddressGrid"> Adresse électronique
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="text"
                        name="exampleEmailGrid"
                        id="exampleEmailGrid"
                        placeholder="foulenbenfoulen@domaine.com"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="exampleEmailGrid">
                        Numéro de téléphone                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="email"
                        name="exampleEmailGrid"
                        id="exampleEmailGrid"
                        placeholder="+216 20 123 123"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="examplePasswordGrid">
                        Date de naissance
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="password"
                        name="examplePasswordGrid"
                        id="examplePasswordGrid"
                        placeholder=""
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>
                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="exampleEmailGrid">
                        Mot de passe
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="password"
                        name="exampleEmailGrid"
                        id="exampleFirstnameGrid"
                        placeholder="foulen"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={6}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label for="examplePasswordGrid">
                        Répeter le mot de passe
                        </Label>
                      <Input
                        type="password"
                        name="exampleLastnameGrid"
                        id="exampleLastnameGrid"
                        placeholder="ben foulen"
                      />
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>
                  
                  <Colxx sm={4}>
                    <FormGroup>
                      <Label>
                        Role
                        </Label>
                      <Input type="select">
                        <option>Responsable</option>
                        <option>Client</option>
                        <option>Employé</option>
                       
                      </Input>
                    </FormGroup>
                  </Colxx>

                  <Colxx sm={12}>

                    <Card>
                      <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle>
                          Photo de l'utilisateur
                </CardTitle>
                        <CustomDropzone />
                      </CardBody>
                    </Card>


                  </Colxx>

                 

                
              
                </FormGroup>

                <Button color="primary">
                  AJOUTER
                  </Button>
              </Form>
            </CardBody>
          </Card>
        </Colxx>
      </Row>
    </Fragment>

  );
}
export default AddUser;
